img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3a014e457037721ff35489f7b9c77ecb7775c8","tid":87344,"uid":71321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T18:14:37.000Z","msg":"阿爸煮海鮮真係一流 同埋從來係食方面唔會孤寒 成日煲花膠湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反阿媽煮野真係狗也不屌 好記得佢之前想整金菇肥牛 但無肥牛賣(佢淨係會去百佳) 所以買左煙肉代替 包完所有野之後佢竟然攞去蒸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d267fd5e2858b256b04ff0d67f4a12a6410751de","tid":87344,"uid":33238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T18:18:36.000Z","msg":"阿爸後生做過幾年廚，所以阿媽同佢無得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過條友好撚懶，一年煮唔夠5次"}]}